Design Document
1. Project Overview

Project Name: User Details Application
Description: This application will collect user details and perform validation, including OTP validation. The frontend will be built using JSP.
2. Requirements

Frontend: JSP for the view
Backend: Spring Boot
Dependencies: Spring Web, Spring Boot Starter JSP, Spring Security (if needed)
3. Architecture

Model-View-Controller (MVC) Architecture
Model: Represents the data (User details).
View: JSP files for the frontend.
Controller: Spring Boot controllers to handle HTTP requests and responses.
4. Components

User: A model class representing the user details.
UserController: Controller class to handle requests.
UserService: Service class to handle business logic and validation.
JSP Pages: Views for the user interface.
